### Basic Fastify Application Setup

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/documentation/otel/metrics.md

A fundamental Fastify web server application without any OpenTelemetry metrics integration. This serves as a baseline for further modifications.

```javascript
'use strict'

const server = require('fastify')({
  logger: {
    level: 'info'
  }
})

server.route({
  path: '/',
  method: 'GET',
  handler (req, res) {
    res.send({ hello: 'world' })
  }
})

server.listen({ port: 8080 })

```

