### Record and Increment Custom Metrics - Node.js

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

This snippet demonstrates how to send custom metrics to New Relic APM using the recordMetric and incrementMetric APIs. These metrics can be viewed on Custom Dashboards. Ensure the New Relic agent is properly configured and running.

```javascript
const newrelic = require('newrelic');

// Record a custom metric with a specific value
newrelic.recordMetric('Custom/MyMetricName', 123.45);

// Increment a custom metric by a value (defaults to 1 if value is omitted)
newrelic.incrementMetric('Custom/MyCounter', 5);
newrelic.incrementMetric('Custom/AnotherCounter'); // Increments by 1
```

